Class OrangeBall

java.lang.Object
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Ball.Ball
com.example.dmscoursework.View.Ball.OrangeBall
public class OrangeBall extends Ball
The OrangeBall class inherits from Ball, so it has access to all the same methods as Ball. However, it has its own makeBall method which allows it to have a unique description.
